title: (Mon Part 1) Kelsea Ballerini In-Studio + Eddie Sees a MAJOR Celeb at Chuck E. Cheese!
itunes:title: (Mon Part 1) Kelsea Ballerini In-Studio + Eddie Sees a MAJOR Celeb at Chuck E. Cheese!
description:
Kelsea Ballerini stops by to talk about “Half of My Hometown”, performing with Dolly Parton at the ACMs, and reveals something surprising about the next phase of her music. Eddie says he saw a major celebrity while out at Chuck E. Cheese and has us guess who it was. Morgan 2 tries to win a caller a prize by naming famous one hit wonders that came before her time.
